<div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">

        <%= image_tag "ML - Profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: "profile-image" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>

          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%=skill.percent_utilized %>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%=skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              ></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Our team has over a decade of development experience in a number of industries.
        In the last years, we follow the ML development and help others to implement what they need.</p>

        <h3>But what is Machine Learning?</h3>

        <p>Machine learning is the idea that there are general algorithms that can tell you something interesting about a set of data without having to write any specific custom code for the problem. Instead of writing the code, the data is fed to a generic algorithm and its logic is constructed based on data.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
            <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 1
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 2
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 3
              </div>
            </div>
  
            <div class="collapse" id="education">
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 1
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 2
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 3
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
      </div>

    </div>


  </div>
  
</div>






